Main Menu:

Add Deck – Create a new deck.

View Decks – Open or edit an existing deck.

Exit – Close the program.

Deck Screen:

Add Card – Add a new flashcard.

Edit/Delete Card – Change or remove a card.

Study Deck – Start studying your cards.

Study Screen:

Spacebar – Flip the card.

Arrow Keys – Move between cards.

Esc – Return to the main menu.

Tips:

Avoid empty names or cards.

Decks save automatically.

Keep names short and simple!
